----------------------------------------
Cheaper Signs (1.8_1)
----------------------------------------

A Minecraft mod that adds a cheaper, more convenient crafting recipe for signs and makes them stackable.

----------------------------------------
Recipes
----------------------------------------

Signs can now be crafted without the use of a crafting table.

P - Plank
| - Stick

.P   or   P.
.|        |.

----------------------------------------
Installation
----------------------------------------

Install ModLoader. Add the two class files and delete META-INF. Enjoy =)
